title: Strange mystery sea creature washes up on Fremantle Beach
text: comments A mystery sea creature has washed up on a Perth beach and left the internet baffled. Images of the slimy dead fish were posted online, with debate amongst social media users quickly developing as to what it could possibly be. The strange creature, which has a huge grey body and white belly, was found decomposing on the shore of Fremantle Beach, Western Australia. Mystery sea creature: A decomposing fish has washed up on a Perth beach and left the internet baffled Some punters were quick to point out that the fish appeared to be missing part of its body on either side, with rough chunks filleted out of the flesh. 'That is spectacular,' one man wrote. 'Kind of looks like a bloated decomposing ray,' added another. RELATED ARTICLES
